OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fthundery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening and pushing eastwards. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier overnight with some clear
OL,9,Fintervals, although low cloud, and
OL,10,Fsome mist and fog patches are likely
OL,11,Fto form. A few showers by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,14,Fwill soon lift to leave sunny spells,
OL,15,Fthough a few showers likely through
OL,16,Fthe morning. Becoming cloudier and
OL,17,Fwindier with rain by the late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
