OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain should have cleared by
OL,7,FThursday morning, with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine developing during the day.
OL,9,FSouthern areas look mostly settled
OL,10,Fthereafter, though some patchy rain
OL,11,Fcould develop further north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
